column2: b'Crayon Shin-chan Movie 06: Dengeki! Buta no Hizume Daisakusen'

b'A full-scale action film with tastes of the "\'007" series and Jackie Chan\'s movies. The members of the secret organization for world peace \'SML\', code-named \'Oiroke\' (sexual attractiveness) and \'Kinniku\' (muscle), who join hands with the Nohara family and Kasukabe Defense Forces (Shinnosuke Nohara and his mates: Kazama-kun, Nene-chan, Masao-kun and Bo-chan), and fight against the evil organization \'Buta no Hizume\' (Pig\'s Hoof), who tries to conquer the world by using a computer virus. \n\n(Source: Manabu Tsuribe)'
